&lt;p&gt;As we grow, we’re seeking skilled, compassionate licensed mental health professionals to join our remote care team. If you&#39;re an &lt;strong&gt;Arizona licensed LCSW, LPC, LMFT, LAC, LAMFT, or LMSW.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;looking to make an impact through virtual care, we’d love to connect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our ability to provide supervision for non-independent mental health professionals varies by state and license, but we also encourage you to apply. We try to support non-independent licensees when possible.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
