&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active and verifiable license from one of the following &lt;strong&gt;Arizona licenses: &amp;nbsp;LCSW, LPC,&amp;nbsp;LMFT,&amp;nbsp;LAC,&amp;nbsp;LAMFT or LMSW. &lt;em&gt;as well as your state of residence if it is not Arizona&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp; All credentials must be verified through the State Board’s website as part of the application process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience providing psychotherapy in outpatient, private practice, or telehealth settings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and clinical skills with a person-centered, trauma-informed approach&lt;/li&gt;
