&lt;li&gt;Provide crisis support and coordinate appropriate referrals when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain timely, accurate documentation in our electronic medical record (EMR) system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with clinical supervisors on individualized treatment and discharge planning&lt;/li&gt;
